            "notes": "The main strategy of this deck is to ramp quickly and efficiently using cards like Exploration, Burgeoning, and Lotus Cobra to accelerate your mana production. With a high land count and cards like Primeval Titan and Sylvan Library, you can consistently hit your land drops and keep your hand full of options. Lumra, Bellow of the Woods serves as a strong aggro commander that can hit hard and fast, putting pressure on your opponent early in the game. Cards like Green Sun's Zenith and Finale of Devastation allow you to tutor for key creatures like Primeval Titan or Emrakul, the Promised End to finish the game quickly. The deck aims to overwhelm your opponent with powerful creatures and efficient ramp, making it a formidable force in Duel Commander 1 vs 1 matchups."
